PrecisEnactment of the SASKATCHEWAN URANIUM MINES AND MILLS EXCLUSION REGULATIONS which extend the province's laws and regulations on occupational safety and health to all uranium mining and milling operations in Saskatchewan that are subject to the federal Nuclear Safety and Control Act.
